  "commentary": "With SPX at 6775.82 sitting just above the 6774 GEX flip and below the massive 6780 gamma wall (28.9B), dealers are in full stabilization mode and should be selling into any push toward 6780 while providing support around 6775. The PIN regime with heavy positive gamma concentration creates a tight trading range between 6775-6780, where mean reversion forces will dominate and cap breakout attempts. The \"wall_break\" event likely triggered additional dealer hedging flows, but the thick gamma walls above should absorb momentum quickly.\n\nKey levels: 6774 flip (regime boundary), 6775 support wall, and 6780 resistance wall where dealers will aggressively sell.\n\nBottom line: expect price to get pinned between 6775-6780 with limited directional movement.",
